</p>

<!-- TEMPLATE: Quick facts table -->
<div class="news-item">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0">Quick Facts</h3>
    <!-- TEMPLATE: Calculator main image -->
    <img src="" alt="[Calculator Name]"
         style="max-width: 400px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 8px auto 16px auto;" />
    <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 4px 8px"><strong>Manufacturer:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 4px 8px">
                <div style="background-color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; padding: 4px 8px;">
                    <!-- TEMPLATE: Replace with manufacturer logo img tag, e.g.:
                         <img src="~/assets/logos/maker-logo.png" alt="[Maker Name]" style="max-height: 30px; height: auto;" />
                    -->
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 8px"><strong>Model:</strong></td><td style="padding: 4px 8px">[Insert model number]</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 8px"><strong>Year Introduced:</strong></td><td style="padding: 4px 8px">[Insert year]</td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding: 4px 8px"><strong>Type:</strong></td><td style="padding: 4px 8px">[Insert type]</td></tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 4px 8px"><strong>Similar Specimens on MyCalcs:</strong></td>
            <td>
                <a href="https://my.calcs.quest/search?models=whatever">https://my.calcs.quest/search?models=whatever</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<!-- TEMPLATE: History / Background -->
<div class="news-item">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0">History &amp; Background</h3>
    <p>
        [This mythical calculator is the greatest calculator in the world.
        There is no greater calculator and there has never been. Never
        will be either. This is the holy grail of calculators.]
    </p>
</div>

